  <div id="wz"><span class="wzword">您的位置：首页 >> 通知公告</span></div>
	<div id="main">	
	
	   <div id="all_content"> 

	     <div class="MainNewsTitle">
	     <h1>医院食堂承包经营招标公告</h1>
	     </div>
				    <div class="MainNewsUpdate">
				      发布时间：2022-08-12
				      
				      信息来源：附属医院　　浏览次数：49393 </div>
				    <div class="MainNewsAction" style="border-bottom: 1px solid #ccc;">
				      <script type="text/javascript">writeColor("common/scripts/color/");</script>
				      【<a href="javascript:doZoom('16px');">大</a> <a href="javascript:doZoom('14px');">中</a> <a href="javascript:doZoom('12px');">小</a>】【<a href="javascript:printWindow();">打印本页</a>】【<a href="javascript:closeWindow();">关闭窗口</a>】</div>
				    <div class="MainNewsAction">
				      
         </div>
				    <div class="MainNewsContent" id="content" style="table-layout:fixed;">&nbsp; &nbsp;<span style="text-indent: 28pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt;">为充分体现公开、公正、公平的原则，为给医院职工、病员及其家属提供一个良好的就餐环境和满意的用餐服务，医院研究决定，现就</span><span style="text-indent: 28pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt;">西藏民族大学附属医院新综合楼餐厅</span><span style="text-indent: 28pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt;">面向社会承包经营进行公开招标。</span>
<p class="p" style="margin: 0pt; text-indent: 0pt; padding: 0pt; line-height: 25pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><b><span style="font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><br />
一、</span></b><b><span style="font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">餐厅食堂</span></b><b><span style="font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">经营的基本服务要求</span></b><b><span style="font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 0, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">&emsp;</span></b><span style="font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 0, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">&emsp;</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 0, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="p" style="margin: 0pt; text-indent: 0pt; padding: 0pt; line-height: 25pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">1、乙方承包的职工</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">食堂</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">，在甲方监督和管理下实行自主经营、自负盈亏，以服务好医院职工和病员就餐为宗旨，通过努力增加菜式品种、提高饭菜质量，物美价廉，薄利多销，改善服务质量，吸引职工就餐等优质服务来增加营业额。</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="p" style="margin: 0pt; text-indent: 0pt; padding: 0pt; line-height: 25pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">2、供应职工、病员及其家属用餐(早、中、晚)，提供点餐、订餐、送餐服务，点餐、订餐、送餐时间相对固定，食堂必须每天定时做好环境卫生清洗工作。&emsp;3、每日菜单公布，明码标价，价格公平，菜品品质必须新鲜，调料瓶必须正规超市或者市场购买，有索证资料。&emsp;&emsp;</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="p" style="margin: 0pt; text-indent: 0pt; padding: 0pt; line-height: 25pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">4、食堂工作人员必须身体健康，工作时服务态度好，严禁发生职工和病员的投诉。&emsp;&emsp;</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="p" style="margin: 0pt; text-indent: 0pt; padding: 0pt; line-height: 25pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">5、中标者签署合同后须缴纳5</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">万</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><font face="宋体">元安全风险抵押金</font><font face="宋体">(无利息)，合同期满后退还。6、接受医院的满意度测评</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">和监督检查</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">，</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">测评或检查不合格</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">，在安全风险押金中扣除</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">500元-1000元</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><font face="宋体">。</font><font face="宋体">&emsp;</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="p" style="margin: 0pt; text-indent: 0pt; padding: 0pt; line-height: 25pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">7、从业人员持证上岗，遵守《中华人民共和国食品安全法》、《中华人民共和国食品安全法实施条例》等法律法规的相关要求。&emsp;&emsp;</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="p" style="margin: 0pt; text-indent: 0pt; padding: 0pt; line-height: 25pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">8、遵守医院的安全生产、消防安全的管理规定，切实履行安全职责。</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="p" style="margin: 0pt; text-indent: 0pt; padding: 0pt; line-height: 25pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">9、</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><font face="宋体">合约期限：</font><font face="宋体">1+1+1（经考核合格可续签2次，最多不超过3年）</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="p" style="margin: 0pt; text-indent: 0pt; padding: 0pt; line-height: 25pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">10、配合医院做好上级部门的要求各项工作，例如：严格执行限塑要求，参加食品安全线上考核，并取得培训合格证明等。</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="p" style="margin: 0pt; text-indent: 0pt; padding: 0pt; line-height: 25pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">11、接受上级部门的检查，并按照要求做好台账资料。</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="p" style="margin: 0pt; text-indent: 0pt; padding: 0pt; line-height: 25pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><b><span style="font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><font face="宋体"><br />
二、投标要求</font><font face="宋体">&emsp;</font></span></b><span style="font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 0, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">&emsp;</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 0, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="p" style="margin: 0pt; text-indent: 0pt; padding: 0pt; line-height: 25pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">1、提供相关营业执照、餐饮许可证、法人身份证、体检证明或健康证、1名驻食堂厨师证。</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="p" style="margin: 0pt; text-indent: 0pt; padding: 0pt; line-height: 25pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">2、投标人在以往餐饮经营中没有任何食品卫生安全、消防安全方面的不良记录。并由当地食品卫生、消防安全主管部门出具证明材料。</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="p" style="margin: 0pt; text-indent: 0pt; padding: 0pt; line-height: 25pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">3、投标前须缴纳投标保证金5千元，由投标人交至</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">西藏民族大学附属医院财务科</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><font face="宋体">。中标人保证金自动转为安全风险抵押金，未中标人的投标保证金评标结束退还。</font><font face="宋体">&emsp;&emsp;</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="p" style="margin: 0pt; text-indent: 0pt; padding: 0pt; line-height: 25pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">4、投标人出现下列情况，其投标保证金将被没收。&emsp;</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="p" style="margin: 0pt; text-indent: 0pt; padding: 0pt; line-height: 25pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">(1)凡是通过资格审查的合格投标人，没有正当理由不得放弃投标，否则，招标人将没收其投标保证金;&emsp;&emsp;</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="p" style="margin: 0pt; text-indent: 0pt; padding: 0pt; line-height: 25pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">(2)投标人在招标文件规定的投标有效期内撤回其投标文件;&emsp;&emsp;</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="p" style="margin: 0pt; text-indent: 0pt; padding: 0pt; line-height: 25pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">(3)中标人未能在规定期限内签署合同协议的;&emsp;&emsp;</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="p" style="margin: 0pt; text-indent: 0pt; padding: 0pt; line-height: 25pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">(4)在招标活动中有违规和违法行为;&emsp;&emsp;</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="p" style="margin: 0pt; text-indent: 0pt; padding: 0pt; line-height: 25pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">(5)法律法规规定的其它情形。&emsp;&emsp;</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="p" style="margin: 0pt; text-indent: 0pt; padding: 0pt; line-height: 25pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">5</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><font face="宋体">、提供食堂经营方案。包括食品安全管理、采购方案</font><font face="宋体">(原材料、食材供应及配送方案)、仓储管理、送餐方案、经营方法(中晚餐主菜品种数量、副食配备是否合理、厨师和服务从业人员的配备、卫生管理、食品留样管理、索证管理、食物中毒应急处理预案等)&emsp;。</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="p" style="margin: 0pt; text-indent: 0pt; padding: 0pt; line-height: 25pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">6</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><font face="宋体">、服务承诺。就经营安全、供应时间、提供餐饮的标准、数量、质量、价格等方面做出病人</font><font face="宋体">(家属)、职工满意度服务承诺。&emsp;&emsp;</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="p" style="margin: 0pt; text-indent: 0pt; padding: 0pt; line-height: 25pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">7</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><font face="宋体">、投标文件正副本各一份，投标人盖章或签名。</font><font face="宋体">&emsp;&emsp;</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="p" style="margin: 0pt; text-indent: 0pt; padding: 0pt; line-height: 25pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">8</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><font face="宋体">、投标报名截止时间，自公告发布之日起五日内有效。</font><font face="宋体">&emsp;&emsp;</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="p" style="margin: 0pt; text-indent: 0pt; padding: 0pt; line-height: 25pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><b><span style="font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><font face="宋体"><br />
三、评标方法：由医院组成评审委员会，根据投标方经营方案、经营优势、服务承诺等方面进行综合评价，通过投票推荐确定。</font><font face="宋体">&emsp;&emsp;</font></span></b><b><span style="font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>
<p class="p" style="margin: 0pt; text-indent: 0pt; padding: 0pt; line-height: 25pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><b><span style="font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><br />
四、双方责任</span></b><span style="font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 0, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">&emsp;&emsp;</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 0, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="p" style="margin: 0pt; text-indent: 0pt; padding: 0pt; line-height: 25pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">(一)甲方责任(医院)&emsp;&emsp;</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="p" style="margin: 0pt; text-indent: 0pt; padding: 0pt; line-height: 25pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">1、甲方提供医院食堂用房及现有设备、炊具用品、餐桌等，甲方将食堂财产清点列单后移交给承包方。&emsp;&emsp;</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="p" style="margin: 0pt; text-indent: 0pt; padding: 0pt; line-height: 25pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">2、甲方提供水、电、空调等给乙方，食堂产生的水电费每月甲方按实际耗用的</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">100</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">%收取。</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="p" style="margin: 0pt; text-indent: 0pt; padding: 0pt; line-height: 25pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">3、甲方对乙方承包食堂的食品卫生、服务质量等方面进行监督。甲方酌情提供力所能及的帮助、指导。&emsp;&emsp;</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="p" style="margin: 0pt; text-indent: 0pt; padding: 0pt; line-height: 25pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">(二)乙方责任(承包人)&emsp;&emsp;</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="p" style="margin: 0pt; text-indent: 0pt; padding: 0pt; line-height: 25pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">1、乙方在遵守国家有关法律法规及医院相关规章制度前提下，提供餐饮服务工作。&emsp;&emsp;</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="p" style="margin: 0pt; text-indent: 0pt; padding: 0pt; line-height: 25pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">2、乙方缴纳的安全风险抵押金，用于违反《中华人民共和国食品安全法》、《中华人民共和国食品安全法实施条例》等法律法规的相关要求、以及甲方的有关安全、财产管理规定、满意度测评等扣款事项。若无上述情形，合同期满后，安全风险抵押金如数退还。&emsp;&emsp;</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="p" style="margin: 0pt; text-indent: 0pt; padding: 0pt; line-height: 25pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">3、在合同期内，乙方不得进行任何形式的转包，若违反，甲方有权无条件终止合同。&emsp;&emsp;</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="p" style="margin: 0pt; text-indent: 0pt; padding: 0pt; line-height: 25pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">4、食堂从业人员由乙方自行安排，工资费用自理，所有聘用人员都必须具备有效健康证明，社保、卫生检疫、体检、人身意外保险等所有运营费用均由乙方自理。&emsp;&emsp;</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="p" style="margin: 0pt; text-indent: 0pt; padding: 0pt; line-height: 25pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">5、食堂每月</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">100</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">%的水费、电费的及日常维修费用均由乙方自行承担，基础性维修由甲方负责。&emsp;&emsp;</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="p" style="margin: 0pt; text-indent: 0pt; padding: 0pt; line-height: 25pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">6、若发生食品安全、消防安全等事故，由此产生的一切责任和损失由乙方负责，甲方有权终止合同。&emsp;&emsp;</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="p" style="margin: 0pt; text-indent: 0pt; padding: 0pt; line-height: 25pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">(三)承包期间，如乙方提前终止合同，须提前一个月通知甲方。甲方如因不可抗原因或主管部门要求提前终止合同，也将提前一个月通知承包人。如承包人未经医院同意，也不在合同规定时间内，单方面提前终止合同，承包人必须承担由此引起的一切经济和法律责任。&emsp;&emsp;</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="p" style="margin: 0pt; text-indent: 0pt; padding: 0pt; line-height: 25pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><b><span style="font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><br />
五、报名方式及开标日期。<br />
</span></b><span style="font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><font face="宋体">&nbsp; 持有效证件书面来医院报名，开标日期另行通知。</font><font face="宋体">&emsp;</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="p" style="margin: 0pt; text-indent: 0pt; padding: 0pt; line-height: 25pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><b><span style="font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><br />
六、</span></b><b><span style="font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">联系人：</span></b><b><span style="font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">赵海同</span></b><b><span style="font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">&nbsp;</span></b><b><span style="font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></b><b><span style="font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">电话：</span></b><b><span style="font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">13629100013 &nbsp;</span></b><b><span style="font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>
<p class="p" style="margin: 0pt; text-indent: 32.15pt; padding: 0pt; line-height: 25pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><b><span style="font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><font face="宋体">地</font> &nbsp;<font face="宋体">点：西藏民族大学附属医院门诊楼三楼后勤保障部</font></span></b><b><span style="font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 16pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>
<p class="p" style="margin: 0pt; text-indent: 0pt; padding: 0pt; line-height: 25pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 12pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="p" style="margin: 0pt; text-indent: 0pt; padding: 0pt; line-height: 25pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 12pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">&nbsp;</span></p>
